des: Therapy is your therapist for Alexa. Tell therapist how you are feeling and she will give you some words of encouragements. Therapy is a lighthearted skill that tries to make your day a little better. Over 500 new moods and words of encouragement!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
